{"tid":1889810,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"十七那年，懵懂無知","createTime":"2020-02-20T22:01:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T18:55:32.000Z","uid":253215,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4394633bc4c79bfeb4e260fdd9e042bc891749ff","tid":1889810,"uid":253215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T22:01:03.000Z","msg":"樓主瞓唔着<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />諗翻起好多嘢，但我嘅文筆唔太掂，寫得衰勿屌。<br />\n<br />\n  仲記得個陣時嘅二月二十，用咗啲小心思，為嘅就只係搵個藉口同你單獨出嚟，令我估唔到嘅，係你居然肯應承。<br />\n<br />\n  唔知係咪太期待同你出，我連續兩個星期都已經瞓唔著，諗嘅係個日出去嘅情況。 <br />\n<br />\n  結果，到咗個日，我哋之間有不斷的話題，同你出去十一個鐘，嗰一日係我願意花光所有口水，為咗同你繼續傾落去，我提議搭叮叮，你一嘢就就應承咗，大慨只有十七，才能由夕陽承搭至皎月，但可惜嘅係你我始終無法成為「百年樹木」中的主角。<br />\n<br />\n  而家諗翻，好想無限loop嗰一日，即使我地嘅關係卻步於曖昧，亦已足夠，個陣嘅青澀大過勇氣，擁有著才害怕失去，最穩定嘅關係，我諗就係陌路人，多謝你，令我學識咗咩叫煎熬咩，咩叫珍惜。"},{"pid":"f1f1146ddeda0837ce47d360ebac14b12ad22754","tid":1889810,"uid":253215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T22:02:17.000Z","msg":"一人攞低一個屬於自己同佢嘅「十七」"},{"pid":"336d82adf2b3d15a3b48e33f36eaff71620a6a02","tid":1889810,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T22:12:40.000Z","msg":"膽粗粗表咗白，然後得不到回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"536c0a258ac22fe0036fceea35ab03bec5fb04e1","tid":1889810,"uid":253215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"336d82adf2b3d15a3b48e33f36eaff71620a6a02","tid":1889810,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T22:12:40.000Z","msg":"膽粗粗表咗白，然後得不到回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T22:28:05.000Z","msg":"有時當面嘅拒絕反而冇沉默咁心酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34b7df7ac594205414cb1666718b9c53dda9bda6","tid":1889810,"uid":46345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T22:59:24.000Z","msg":"down咗套A片<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b6f960e4ab6ffe291306d1e8fb93736e2ee9fc6","tid":1889810,"uid":239672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T23:10:03.000Z","msg":"17 歲嗰年會考 <br />\n佢讀隔離班 成日借d 椅過去扮揾friend  偷望下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一大半嘅中學生涯都係暗戀佢嘅時光下度過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nlast day同佢影完合照之後就十幾年冇見<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次見返張相都好心動<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e39311b4fe7a3e370839bf2fe48c330edf06ed26","tid":1889810,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"536c0a258ac22fe0036fceea35ab03bec5fb04e1","tid":1889810,"uid":253215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"336d82adf2b3d15a3b48e33f36eaff71620a6a02","tid":1889810,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T22:12:40.000Z","msg":"膽粗粗表咗白，然後得不到回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T22:28:05.000Z","msg":"有時當面嘅拒絕反而冇沉默咁心酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T23:25:03.000Z","msg":"沒錯，可能我根本唔應該表白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee5ce8e6de1ba2691fa56e7bbbbcd54182d53c0","tid":1889810,"uid":15251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T05:36:08.000Z","msg":"明明大家都係中意對方<br />\n但係一個冇膽一個唔夠堅持<br />\n最後錯過左對方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9786ed024ef591615bea93faad151ceba4e97079","tid":1889810,"uid":42927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T05:41:51.000Z","msg":"我係一件垃圾<br />\n我冇撚用呀<br />\n我唔死都冇撚用呀<br />\n嗚嗚嗚⋯⋯"},{"pid":"74ec47c6228ae2049e5a58bf6890e83ade10f508","tid":1889810,"uid":337596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T18:55:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}